        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14847059/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14847059/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54920444/" class=" " title="云蔚">云蔚</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14847059">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">记的余秋雨某文中，提到过日本某将在要间系一牌，上面写的就是这句，“一生伏首拜阳明”。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14847059/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-10-11 22:05</span>
                  
                </p>
